name: Farm & Ranch No-Flat Utility Wheel - 10 Inch
description: This 10 in. no-flat replacement wheel comes with heavy-duty ball bearings and a 5/8 in. bore. The solid polyurethane design means this wheel will not need air and you will never be stuck with a flat tire. This 10 in. wheel is works great as a replacement or an alternative to regular air-filled tires.
